issue.title: plugin: redirects to "login" page (in metamask context)
issue.body:
When event has been identified or uploaded and CID is known: redirect to the event-wallet app
with 

?cid=cid&url=urlencode(current url)

+ on mobile it should deeplink into the metamask browser if installed. 
maybe it's https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-681 or https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-681 maybe it's impossible.
